==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wide-awake
<hw>Wide`-a*wake"</hw> <pr>(w⟦imac⟧d`⟦adot⟧*w⟦amac⟧k")</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <def>Fully awake; not drowsy or dull; hence, knowing;
keen; alert.</def> <rj><au>Dickens.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wide-awake</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Wide-awake
<hw>Wide`-a*wake"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A broad-brimmed, low-crowned
felt hat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

